# ⚛️ Frontend (React)

## ✅ Important Rule

For cookies to work:

```js
credentials: "include"
```

***

## 3️⃣ Helper to read CSRF cookie

```js
function getCookie(name) {
  return document.cookie
    .split("; ")
    .find(row => row.startsWith(name + "="))
    ?.split("=")[1];
}
```

***

## 4️⃣ Login.jsx

```jsx
